item.title: Tue, 27 Oct 2020 08:47:37 UTC
item.description:
Hi Folks,
After upgrading to python 3.9 and Alien's decision not to upgrade ktown,
I have decided to suspend publishing the packages, as I use ktwon and
therefore cannot test well the packages I create in the clean install.
While waiting for Pat to add Plasma5 to the current one soon, best regards.
I'm sorry for my bad english. Happy slacking!

	- Don't build on current anymore. I started using appimage version.
